lead_paragraph: Jordan Morris scored his 11th and 12th goals of his rookie season and the Seattle Sounders beat the Los Angeles Galaxy 4-2 on Sunday to snap an 11-game road winless streak in the series.

headline.print_headline: Sounders Win at Galaxy for 1st Time Since 2009
